<subSubSection id="47A22ED7FF9CFFE6FF24FEA64E17FDAD" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0F077D5CFF9CFFE6FF24FEA64E17FDAD" blockId="6.[178,1086,345,563]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">
Comment: 
<taxonomicName id="C8B806DFFF9CFFE6FEF3FEA64E05FEF1" baseAuthorityName="ROUGEMONT" baseAuthorityYear="1986" box="[357,600,345,367]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Stilicoderus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="assamensis">
<emphasis id="3DCCA14EFF9CFFE6FEF3FEA64E05FEF1" box="[357,600,345,367]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">Stilicoderus assamensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF9CFFE6FC8DFEA54FAAFEF1" author="ROUGEMONT G" box="[795,1015,345,367]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" pagination="139 - 187" refId="ref7740" refString="ROUGEMONT G. de (1986 a): Revision of the genus Stiliderus MOTSCHULSKY, 1858, Part I: (= Stilicoderus SHARP, 1889) (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Paederinae). - Entomologische Abhandlungen 49: 139 - 187." type="journal article" year="1986">ROUGEMONT (1986a)</bibRefCitation>
, based on a single male from 
<collectingRegion id="CD7CB3BEFF9CFFE6FE25FE894DB5FE15" box="[435,488,374,395]" country="Philippines" name="Naga" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">Naga</collectingRegion>
Hills (
<collectingRegion id="CD7CB3BEFF9CFFE6FDACFE8A4ED9FE15" box="[570,644,373,395]" country="India" name="Assam" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">Assam</collectingRegion>
), and subsequently synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="C8B806DFFF9CFFE6FBBCFE894E43FE39" authority="(SCHEERPELTZ 1965)" baseAuthorityName="SCHEERPELTZ" baseAuthorityYear="1965" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Stilicoderus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kambaitiensis">
<emphasis id="3DCCA14EFF9CFFE6FBBCFE894D60FE39" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">S. kambaitiensis</emphasis>
(SCHEERPELTZ 1965)
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF9CFFE6FDDCFE6D4F75FE39" author="ROUGEMONT G" box="[586,808,401,423]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" pagination="233 - 236" refId="ref7785" refString="ROUGEMONT G. de (1986 b): New records of Stiliderus from Nepal (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). 21 st contribution to the knowledge of Staphylinidae. - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 93 (1): 233 - 236." type="journal article" year="1986">ROUGEMONT (1986b)</bibRefCitation>
. The aedeagi of the males of the above material are in absolute agreement with the illustration of the aedeagus of the 
<typeStatus id="D003C3FEFF9CFFE6FF4DFE364D69FE41" box="[219,308,457,479]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">holotype</typeStatus>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF9CFFE6FECCFE354E67FE41" author="ROUGEMONT G" box="[346,570,457,479]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" pagination="139 - 187" refId="ref7740" refString="ROUGEMONT G. de (1986 a): Revision of the genus Stiliderus MOTSCHULSKY, 1858, Part I: (= Stilicoderus SHARP, 1889) (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Paederinae). - Entomologische Abhandlungen 49: 139 - 187." type="journal article" year="1986">ROUGEMONT (1986a)</bibRefCitation>
. A comparison with material of 
<taxonomicName id="C8B806DFFF9CFFE6FC03FE354860FE41" baseAuthorityName="SCHEERPELTZ" baseAuthorityYear="1965" box="[917,1085,457,479]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Stilicoderus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kambaitiensis">
<emphasis id="3DCCA14EFF9CFFE6FC03FE354860FE41" box="[917,1085,457,479]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">S. kambaitiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from various regions revealed distinct and constant differences in the shape of the ventral process and the shapes of the apical internal structures, so that there is little doubt that 
<taxonomicName id="C8B806DFFF9CFFE6FBBCFDFD4D79FDAD" baseAuthorityName="ROUGEMONT" baseAuthorityYear="1986" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Stilicoderus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="assamensis">
<emphasis id="3DCCA14EFF9CFFE6FBBCFDFD4D79FDAD" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="1577">S. assamensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represents a distinct species.
</paragraph>
